:Theme_HumanPowerAndLimits a :Theme ;
  :description "The ode celebrates human ingenuity while stressing moral and existential limits."^^xsd:string .

:Theme_LawAndCity a :Theme ;
  :description "Belonging to the city depends on respecting law and justice."^^xsd:string .

:Theme_ForeshadowingAntigone a :Theme ;
  :description "The chorus' reflection shifts toward recognition of Antigone's transgression."^^xsd:string .
